snippet.title: State of Decay 2: Juggernaut Edition Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
State of Decay 2: Juggernaut Edition re-imagines the popular zombie game as a brand-new experience for both new and veteran players. This edition is packed with new updates including remastered graphics, a new tutorial, a new open-world map and new heavy weapons to bust zombie heads.

https://www.xbox.com/games/state-of-decay-2

Audio Description: https://youtu.be/Y0tycQPX8iI
